Class Apartment

  • java.lang.Object
    • padsof.Apartment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Apartment
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    Alejandro Santorum y David Cabornero This class allows to create a new apartment of a Landlord, get and set its attributes (the postal code, the address, the description and the Landlord) and return this class as a string.
